# Design system (Project Braids)

Read `reference/design/visual-identity-and-ux.md` before UI work.

- **Mobile-first:** design small screen first; min 44px touch targets
- **Stack:** Tailwind + shadcn/ui themed to project tokens (gold `#B8860B`, Fraunces + DM Sans)
- **Components:** one primary CTA per viewport; skeleton loading; status = text + colour
- **Dashboard:** bottom nav on mobile; escalations highest priority
- **AI UI:** purple accent `#6B4C9A`; label AI on first interaction
- **a11y:** WCAG 2.1 AA, focus rings, `aria-live` for dynamic updates
- British English copy; warm, direct tone
